### Batch G — Grid Widget  *(depends on A, D)*

- [x] **G1** `ui/grid_widget.py`: extract `_move_selection(dr, dc)` — clamps to `[0, size-1]` (no wrap), skips black cells.
- [x] **G2** `ui/grid_widget.py`: `_advance_selection(delta, skip_black=True)` — skips black cells row-major.
