## Performance & Hardening
- Benchmarks for solver/validator (<200ms validate, <2s solve 9x9) and persistence (<300ms typical); profile hot paths.
- SE grader benchmark: `grade()` < 100ms for typical 9x9; cage permutation safe for cages > 5 cells.
- Memory guards for undo/redo and candidate tracking (esp. 1–25).
- Robust error handling for malformed imports; deterministic seeds in tests.
- Documentation: architecture, data formats, extension points, usage.

## Future-ready Hooks
- Stubs/hooks for puzzle editor, online sharing, multiplayer, cloud saves, mobile-friendly UI.
- Theming extensibility for future palette/fonts; English-only baseline with i18n hooks.
- Additional solver optimizations for larger grids.

